      "content": "those are good, thanks. i'm worried though, some of my regular customers are pretty old school and might see the word 'equity' or 'DEI' and think we're getting too political. maybe u can give me some options that focus more on just being 'friendly to everyone' without using all the formal DEI terminology? like something more subtle?",
